Ne, pletete se.

562
00:41:41,080 --> 00:41:44,170
Tam ryby nejsou.

563
00:41:44,960 --> 00:41:46,800
A kde teda jsou?

564
00:41:48,550 --> 00:41:50,220
V kartách...

565
00:41:53,050 --> 00:41:54,970
V kartách...

566
00:41:56,560 --> 00:42:01,230
